<seg id="74">A music school with 100 students has become a focal point for the community of Vicente Guerrero in Oaxaca. </seg>
<seg id="75">The British newspaper The Guardian wrote about the project: </seg>
<seg id="76">The community, in one of Mexico’s poorest states, has a reputation for drug abuse and gang violence. </seg>
