<seg id="823">However, it does raise questions about our appetite for images with news. </seg>
<seg id="824">What happened in the Democratic Republic of Congo </seg>
<seg id="825">In 2010, a fuel tanker traveling through Sange, a town in Eastern DRC, overturned and exploded, killing over 230 people. </seg>
